CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FWith the Senedd Election just three
OL,8,Fweeks away, Wales' larger political
OL,9,Fparties have now put their cards on
OL,10,Fthe table and published manifestos
OL,11,Fthat define their pitch to voters.
OL,13,FThe six larger political parties in
OL,14,FWales are: Plaid Cymru, Reform UK,
OL,15,FWelsh Labour, Green Party, Welsh
OL,16,FConservatives, and Welsh Liberal
OL,17,FDemocrats.
OL,19,FOn 7 May, members of the public can
OL,20,Fvote for either a political party or
OL,21,Fan independent candidate.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FThe cost-of-living and inflation came
OL,8,Ftop of the list of priorities in ITV
OL,9,FCymru Wales' latest opinion polls with
OL,10,F51% of people saying it is among the
OL,11,Fmost important issues for them.
OL,13,FThe first party to kick things off at
OL,14,Fthe start of March was the Welsh
OL,15,FConservatives, unveiling their plans
OL,16,Fat the St David's Hotel in Cardiff.
OL,18,FThe Welsh Conservatives pledge to cut
OL,19,Fthe basic rate of income tax by 1p and
OL,20,Fscrap stamp duty in Wales if they are
OL,21,Felected in May.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FLeader Darren Millar said his income
OL,8,Ftax policy would be "a direct saving
OL,9,Fof #450 per year for the average
OL,10,Fworking family".
OL,12,FReform UK also pledged a similar
OL,13,Foffering to cut 1p off every #1 across
OL,14,Fall rates of Welsh income tax, to
OL,15,F"jump start the Welsh economy".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FDuring their manifesto launch, leader
OL,8,FDan Thomas said that unlike the
OL,9,FConservatives "our income tax cut is
OL,10,Fscheduled for the last year of our
OL,11,Fterm, whereas theirs is scheduled for
OL,12,Fmuch earlier and I think that's really
OL,13,Funrealistic."
OL,15,FHis party has also promised to
OL,16,Fintroduce referendums for council tax
OL,17,Frises above 4.99%, as a means of
OL,18,Flowering the cost-of-living.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FHe said: "Council tax is one of the
OL,8,Flargest household bills for most
OL,9,Ffamilies, Welsh councils have been
OL,10,Ffleecing residents with an average
OL,11,Fcouncil tax increase of over 7%.
OL,12,FReform will end this extortion."
OL,14,FWelsh Labour has pledged to not raise
OL,15,Frates of income tax, if their party
OL,16,Fleads the next Welsh Government.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FSpeaking at her party's manifesto
OL,8,Flaunch in Swansea, leader Eluned
OL,9,FMorgan MS, said: "I make a clear
OL,10,Fpromise to the people of Wales: in the
OL,11,Fnext Senedd term a Welsh Labour
OL,12,FGovernment will not raise income tax.
OL,14,F"Fairness starts with understanding
OL,15,Fthe pressure families face but
OL,16,Ffairness also means action."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FCurrently, the Welsh Government has
OL,8,Fthe power to vary income tax by ten
OL,9,Fpercentage points but so far it has
OL,10,Fnot made use of its income tax powers
OL,11,Fto increase or reduce rates.
OL,13,FThe only party to say they will
OL,14,Fincrease Welsh income tax is the Welsh
OL,15,FLiberal Democrats, who will put 1p on
OL,16,FWelsh income tax to invest in the
OL,17,Fhealth service.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FThe Welsh Liberal Democrats' top five
OL,8,Fpriorities do not explicitly reference
OL,9,Fthe "cost-of-living" although it is
OL,10,Fmentioned in their explanation of
OL,11,Fnumber three priority - "Help Wales
OL,12,Fthrive".
OL,14,FThey argue that by "working with our
OL,15,Fcolleagues across the UK to get the
OL,16,Feconomy growing," they can "end the
OL,17,Fcost-of-living by helping people get
OL,18,Fback to work". This includes helping
OL,19,Fpeople get back into work by
OL,20,F"retraining, cutting NHS waiting lists
OL,21,Fand helping family carers work".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FPlaid Cymru's leader have taken a
OL,8,Fdifferent approach to tackling the
OL,9,Fcost-of-living, turning to helping
OL,10,Ffamilies "through affordable, quality
OL,11,Fchildcare".
OL,13,F"We'll support families and give every
OL,14,Fchild the best possible start through
OL,15,Fa transformational new free childcare
OL,16,Foffer for all children aged nine
OL,17,Fmonths to four-years-old," Rhun ap
OL,18,FIorwerth said.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FThe Greens have prioritised a number
OL,8,Fof cost-of-living pledges. Notably,
OL,9,Freplacing council tax with land value
OL,10,Ftax to try and ensure "wealthier
OL,11,Fproperty owners pay more".
OL,13,FHealth came a close second behind the
OL,14,Fcost-of-living in the list of
OL,15,Fpriorities identified in the latest
OL,16,Fopinion poll, with 46% of respondents
OL,17,Fsaying it was among their top issues.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FOne of the biggest talking points over
OL,8,Fthe past year on the health agenda has
OL,9,Fbeen corridor care and cutting waiting
OL,10,Flists.
OL,12,FNew figures revealed almost 89,000
OL,13,Fpatients were treated in corridors or
OL,14,Fother non-clinical environments
OL,15,Fbetween 2022 and the end of October
OL,16,F2025 in hospitals run by Betsi
OL,17,FCadwaladr University Health Board
OL,18,Falone.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FThe Green Party has pledged to end
OL,8,F"corridor care" in Wales by declaring
OL,9,Fsuch incidents as "never-events".
OL,11,FTheir plan states that caring for a
OL,12,Fpatient in a chair for more than 24
OL,13,Fhours should be classified as a "never-
OL,14,Fevent" requiring immediate reporting.
OL,16,FThe Welsh Conservatives have also
OL,17,Fcalled for the 12-hour mark to be the
OL,18,Fthreshold for a "never-event."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FCompared to Reform however, who said
OL,8,Fthat only by the end of their four-
OL,9,Fyear term would corridor care be
OL,10,Fclassed as a "reportable safety
OL,11,Fincident".
OL,13,FReform's number one priority for
OL,14,Fhealthcare in Wales is implementing a
OL,15,Fstrategy for cutting waiting lists,
OL,16,Fwith plans to launch an emergency
OL,17,Faction plan and open "rapid diagnostic
OL,18,Fcentres".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FWelsh Labour's manifesto did not
OL,8,Fmention corridor care specifically but
OL,9,Fit set out what they had already done
OL,10,Fwhilst in power, such as keeping
OL,11,Fprescriptions free and "delivering
OL,12,Frecord-breaking reductions in long
OL,13,Fwaiting times".
OL,15,FMoving forward, Labour have pledged to
OL,16,Finvest #4 billion in a "Hospitals of
OL,17,Fthe Future Fund" to build new
OL,18,Fhospitals including replacing Wales'
OL,19,Flargest hospital in the country,
OL,20,FUniversity Hospital of Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FThe Welsh Liberal Democrats put
OL,8,Fprotecting the NHS as one of their
OL,9,Ffive priorities for Wales, with
OL,10,Fcorridor care at the top of that
OL,11,Fagenda.
OL,13,FThe party's plans for tackling the
OL,14,Fissue is investing up to 5,000 new or
OL,15,Frefurbished nursing-care placements in
OL,16,Fa bid to help hospitals focus on
OL,17,Ftreating patients and bringing down
OL,18,Fwaiting lists.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FWith more than seven pages on health
OL,8,Fin their manifesto, Plaid Cymru said
OL,9,Fthey have a "radical plan" for
OL,10,Frenewing the NHS in Wales.
OL,12,FKicking things off with tackling
OL,13,Fwaiting lists, Plaid outlined that in
OL,14,FWales more than 5,000 patients are
OL,15,Fwaiting more than two years for
OL,16,Ftreatment, compared with fewer than
OL,17,F200 in England.
OL,19,FPlaid's answer to corridor care is
OL,20,Fincreasing the number of beds on Welsh
OL,21,Fhospital wards.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46517
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FImmigration and asylum came third in
OL,8,Fthe list of priorities in an ITV Cymru
OL,9,FWales poll. 25% of people said it was
OL,10,Famong the issues that were most
OL,11,Fimportant to them.
OL,13,FPowers and decisions over immigration
OL,14,Fand asylum are not devolved to Wales.
OL,15,FIt remains the responsibility of the
OL,16,FUK Government at Westminster.
OL,17,FNevertheless, it is clearly important
OL,18,Fto voters and all the parties have a
OL,19,Fposition related to it.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G17/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46518
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FReform UK has put ending the 'Nation
OL,8,For Sanctuary' policy in their core
OL,9,Fpledges, stating they would scrap the
OL,10,Fuse of "migrant hotels" and
OL,11,Finternational aid in Wales,
OL,12,Fprioritising Welsh men and women for
OL,13,Fsocial housing.
OL,15,FThey explain that would mean a "10-
OL,16,Fyear residency requirement for social
OL,17,Fhousing to put Welsh citizens at the
OL,18,Ffront of the queue", although this
OL,19,Fwould be waived for some vulnerable
OL,20,Findividuals.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G18/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46519
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FThe plan was introduced in 2019 to
OL,8,Fprovide support for refugees and
OL,9,Fasylum seekers, including help
OL,10,Faccessing health services and advice
OL,11,Fon integration - with the vast
OL,12,Fmajority of the money spent supporting
OL,13,FUkrainian refugees.
OL,15,FMr Farage previously confirmed that a
OL,16,FReform-led Welsh Government would have
OL,17,Fa bespoke scheme for Ukrainian
OL,18,Frefugees in Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G19/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46520
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FSimilarly, the Welsh Conservatives
OL,8,Fsaid they would also scrap the Nation
OL,9,Fof Sanctuary.
OL,11,FBoth the Green Party and Welsh Labour
OL,12,Fcommitted to maintaining the policy.
OL,14,FAlthough the Liberal Democrats omitted
OL,15,Fthe policy from their manifesto,
OL,16,FLeader Jane Dodds has voiced her
OL,17,F"wholehearted support" for the Nation
OL,18,Fof Sanctuary.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G20/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46521
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FPlaid Cymru called for devolved powers
OL,8,Fover migration in order to deliver a
OL,9,F"fair" rules-based system to reflect
OL,10,Fthe needs of Wales. But also said it
OL,11,Fdoes not support open borders or
OL,12,Funcontrolled migration.
OL,14,FJust under 20% of people in a recent
OL,15,FITV Cymru's poll said education should
OL,16,Fone of the priorities of the next
OL,17,FWelsh Government.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G21/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46522
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FIn January, Wales' National Children's
OL,8,FLaureates warned of a "crisis" in
OL,9,Fliteracy in schools, publishing an
OL,10,Fopen letter urging the current and
OL,11,Fupcoming government to take immediate
OL,12,Faction in response to the fall in
OL,13,Fliteracy levels and reading for
OL,14,Fpleasure among children and young
OL,15,Fpeople.
OL,17,FIn 2022, Wales' PISA scores in
OL,18,Freading, maths, and science fell to
OL,19,Ftheir lowest levels ever - well below
OL,20,Fthe national average across the UK.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G22/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46523
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FPlaid Cymru has said raising these
OL,8,Fscores "is one of the most urgent
OL,9,Fchallenges our education system faces"
OL,10,Fand have developed what they call a
OL,11,F"Foundational Literacy and Numeracy
OL,12,FPlan".
OL,14,FTo achieve their aims they have set
OL,15,Fout various goals such as providing
OL,16,Flibrary spaces in every primary school
OL,17,Fby 2030 and supporting teachers in
OL,18,Fimplementing the curriculum.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G23/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46524
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FWelsh Labour claimed in their
OL,8,Fmanifesto that they have "radically
OL,9,Freformed education in Wales" but
OL,10,Facknowledged "it remains under
OL,11,Fpressure".
OL,13,FTheir top pledge under education is to
OL,14,Fboost standards in schools "through a
OL,15,Frelentless focus on excellence in
OL,16,Fliteracy and numeracy".
OL,18,FReform UK claimed that one of the
OL,19,Freasons for dropping education
OL,20,Fstandards in Wales is "classroom
OL,21,Fdisruption".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G24/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46525
SC,0025
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FThey said they will change the
OL,8,Fcurriculum in Wales to ensure it
OL,9,Ffocusses more on subjects like maths
OL,10,Fand science, removing "ideological
OL,11,Fcontent" in lessons "under the banner
OL,12,Fof wellbeing or social justice".
OL,14,FWhilst also taking a "zero-tolerance"
OL,15,Fapproach to discipline and banning
OL,16,Fphones in schools.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G25/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46526
SC,0026
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FThe Green Party also plans to make
OL,8,Fschools "phone-free environments" and
OL,9,Fsaid they would provide more support
OL,10,Fto teachers by increasing planning and
OL,11,Fpreparation time from 10 to 15%.
OL,13,FThe Welsh Conservatives also looked to
OL,14,F"restore discipline" in schools
OL,15,Fthrough driving up school attendance
OL,16,Fand banning mobile phones. The party
OL,17,Falso looked to introduce automatically
OL,18,Fexpelling pupils in possession of
OL,19,Fknives and other weapons.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G26/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
