FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46527
SC,0027
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1776780668
OL,3,CKey pledges from the six larger
OL,4,Cpolitical parties ahead of Senedd
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FTopping the Liberal Democrats'
OL,8,Feducation agenda is a real-terms
OL,9,Fincrease in per-pupil funding and the
OL,10,Fprovision of free school meals to
OL,11,Feligible children during school
OL,12,Fholidays, although the manifesto does
OL,13,Fnot clarify who would qualify for this
OL,14,Fsupport.
OL,16,FThe full party manifestos can found on
OL,17,Fthe respective party's websites and
OL,18,Fare available in both Welsh and
OL,19,FEnglish.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G27/29
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
